source.name: State of the Cities Data Systems (SOCDS)
source.description: The SOCDS provides data for individual Metropolitan Areas, Central Cities, and Suburbs, including demographic and economic statistics, employment, county business patterns, FBI crime data, and local building permits. Definitions of criteria, methodologies, and statistically defined areas are provided.
